</div>
<div>
<p>遷宮苑副使<pc>，</pc>出為高陽關及<placeName>鎮</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>魏</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>並</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>代<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>趙</placeName>
<measure quantity="5" unit="prefectures">
<num value="5">五</num>州</measure>
<term>都監</term>
<pc>。</pc>
